@node p119-info " The Party 5 - Information"
@toc p119


    @{b}The Party 5 - Information @{ub}


    You can access information about this party from:

    E-Mail         theparty@cybernet.dk


    3400 visitors attended this party (party place: 20000 m˛).


    @{b}The problem with the correct results @{ub}

     The organisers  even  seemed  to be  not capable to
     unite a  few groups in  a small text;  the official
     results only  included some vague  names of the de-
     signers.  We hope  we succeeded  in finding out the
     correct results sometimes anyway ...



    A CD-Rom with all  released stuff was released after
    The Party 5.



    @{b}New viruses on The Party 5 @{ub}

    Some versions of TP5-TSL.LHA and TP5-TRSI.LHA include
    the new Trojan Virus.  JS!BS1&2.LHA includes somekind
    of a harddisk-formatter.
@endnode

