@node d0020
@toc p008-demo

@{b}
    Enigma
@{ub}

     Producer  : Phenomena

     Coder     : Azatoth
     Graphician: Uno
     Sounder   : Firefox, Tip

     Size      : 437K
     System    : OCS, 1Mb Ram
     How2Handle: CPU Cache off, OCS Chipset on

     Genre     : Diskdemo


     WhatIsIt? : No question about it: This IS the most CLASSIC and
                 the most FAMOUS demo of all time. Of course it does
                 not normally go into a Top-50 nowadays, but it is
                 just too nostalgic to be left out. I remember how
                 astonished I was when I watched this demo for the 
                 very first time. I guess that PHENOMENA is yet today
                 the group that most people wants to see a "comeback"
                 from. There have been a lot of rumours that they
                 really will do a comeback but I doubt it myself.
                 Whatever happens, PHENOMENA will always be among the
                 true legends of the Amiga-scene and all scenes in 
                 general! (Wizard)
@endnode

