@{b}
    Logic
@{ub}

     Producer  : Pygmy Projects

     Coder     : Flame, Silver Eagle
     Graphician: Flame, Silver Eagle
     Sounder   : Paralogic System
     Designer  : Flame

     Size      : 526K (#1) + 799K (#2); 2500K (HD)
     System    : 6Mb Ram, AGA, 2Mb ChipMem, HD-installable; MC68030 recommended
     How2Handle: Exit

     Genre     : Multifile-Demo (HD) (2d)


     WhatIsIt? : All top-3 demos from the Assembly'95 looked the same.
                 And  they also  had demands  of fast  CPU's to really
                 enjoy  the demo.  Complex objects  and not much  of a
                 real demo  in my opinion.  Leave this  kind of  demos
                 to the PC!                        (Wizard)
@endnode

