@{ub}
     Producer  : Oxyron

     Coder     : TTS, Axis, Graham
     Graphician: Gandalf
     Sounder   : No-XS

     Size      : 736K (#1) + 368K (#2)
     System    : 2Mb ChipMem, 3,8Mb FastMem, HD
     How2Handle: 1) start demo by Icon Exorcism_Start
                 2) the demo needs a clear boot
                 3) if you have less than 3,8Mb FastMem after loading
                    Workbench then start the demo by booting without
                    startup-sequence, then assign with "assign exorcism:"
                    and start with "exorcism:exorcism.exe"

     Genre     : Diskdemo (2d)


     WhatIsIt? : Not bad. The doom routine separates this demo 
                 from lots of others. (Dr.Dreyer)
@endnode

