    Rabies
@{ub}

     Producer  : Rage

     Coder     : Digimatic, Rubber, Spirou, Cuddley
     Graphician: Foxx
     Sounder   : Fajser

     Size      : 688K (#1) + 471K (#2) + 605K (#3); 1,8Mb (HD-version)
     System    : AGA, 2Mb ChipMem, HD-installable

     Genre     : Diskdemo (3d)


     WhatIsIt? : An atmospheric, if gory beginning to this demo gives it
                 a flying start. Generally speaking, it contains effects
                 that have been done before,  but has done them so well,
                 and so smooth  (even on a  standard A1200).  Colourful,
                 flowing, and well presented. (Kenji Irie)

                 One of the most atmospheric demos ever, nice music 
                 (timed) and graphic, nice routines! 
                 Especially for Sci-Fi fans.   (Dr.Dreyer)
@endnode

