@node d1551
@toc p190-demo

@{b}
    Poszîy Konie po Betonie
@{ub}

     Producer  : Przyjaciele Stefana B.

     Coder     : Mroova, Skafander

     System    : AGA, 2Mb ChipMem, 1Mb FastMem, HD (1,5Mb free memory)

     Genre     : Multifile-Demo (HD)


     WhatIsIt? : Obviously made for fun (I hope so!)! You have to
                 understand Polish to understand the song (and most
                 people don't), which is probably funny. The only
                 thing that saves this demo IS the music, that is
                 if you understand the Polish language. Else nothing
                 saves it! The graphic is very UGLY! It's a lot of
                 pictures which looks like my very first drawings in
                 DPaint. I would call this an ugly "slideshow" with 
                 strange sounds...

                 Boy it's ugly :)! Probably funny?      (Dr.Dreyer)
@endnode

