@node d1664
@toc p164-demo

@{b}
    Twin Peaks
@{ub}

     Producer  : TRSI

     Coder     : The Twins
     Graphician: Noogman/Artwork
     Sounder   : Virgill

     Size      : 1900K
     System    : AGA, 2Mb ChipMem, HD, 4Mb FastMem; 68030 recommended; no A4000
     How2Handle: You HAVE to use CURSOR KEYS (walk  around)
                 and `+` `#` (going up/down) to control the
                 2nd effect, the Textured-Voxel!

     Genre     : Multifile-Demo (HD)


     WhatIsIt? : Although stated from the authors that this is only
                 a beta-version, the demo is quite cool, showing
                 really good voxels and other nice effects. Not a
                 mega-hit, but without any doubt a big one. 
                 The sleeping gods are back in town! (Dire)
@endnode

