     Producer  : Contraz

     Coder     : Skjeggspir, Zelow, Brekke, Enex
     Graphician: Mr.Figaro, Nirvana, Dran
     Sounder   : Fro-D, Pinnochio
     Designer  : Enex, Corrupt

     Size      : 749K
     System    : AGA, 6Mb Ram, HD; not compatible with A4000; 68030 recommended
     How2Handle: boot without startup-sequence with setpatch

     Genre     : Multifile-Demo (HD) (file)


     WhatIsIt? : If your eyes update just as slow as the routines
                 in this demo it might look nice... (Dr.Dreyer)
@endnode

@node d1912
@toc p218-demo

@{b}
    Mnemonic
@{ub}

     Producer  : Ephidrena

     Coder     : Cyberstarr, Loaderror
     Graphician: Loaderror, Cheetah, Micro/Kinky
     Sounder   : Frequent

     System    : AGA, 4Mb Ram

     Genre     : Multifile-Demo (HD)


     WhatIsIt? : Must have been a small party since it was placed
                 2nd... Most of routines are a little too slow to
                 be nice (for example a rotating texture-tunnel, a
                 "party twister" and some nice but slow "rings in
                 water" effects). Furthermore there's a transparent
                 skull and a plasma-like effect which is mirrored.
                 The music is a piece of "dreamy" techno, the
                 graphic is below average. (Dr.Dreyer)
@endnode

