@{b}
    Massive Killing Capacity
@{ub}

     Producer  : Ram Jam

     Coder     : Randy, Klorathy
     Graphician: Loop, Iliam, Randy
     Sounder   : Klorathy

     System    : AGA, 2Mb ChipMem, 4Mb FastMem, HD

     Genre     : Multifile-Demo (HD)


     WhatIsIt? : Was disqualified by the jury selecting the demos at the
                 Assembly '96! The reason why, is (source: ROM 8):
                 "Eye Q & Stargazer, both jury experts, thought that the
                 Ram Jam contribution was way too ugly to present to the
                 masses". I don't understand that (neither do Ram Jam and
                 many others)! This demo is good! If it really IS true
                 that that was what happened, they (the jury) should leave 
                 the Scene forever (or stop being bribed!)!   (Dr.Dreyer)
@endnode

